
= toolkit under construction by the [[Sharitories]] project

URL = http://www.sharitories.net/


=Description=

"The Collaborative Territories Toolkit will be based on contributions and best practices from across the globe, collected from thought leaders and practitioners who work to speed up the transition towards a collaborative society. This initiative was born thanks to the support of our main founding partner Forum PA: the first draft of the Collaborative Territories Toolkit will be presented and elaborated during a workshop organised during the Smart City Exhibition in Bologna, held between 22-24 October 2014, a conference organised by Forum PA and other partners."

